name: Maze Eater (Cascade Games)
overview: A game from the notorious Cassette 50. It has the distinction of being the first game on every version of the Cassette 50 compilation with the sole exception of the ZX Spectrum release. In this Pac-Man inspired game, you play the titular Pac-Man like character and have to eat all the dots in the maze while avoiding the ghost (there's only one) within the maze.
